      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI DATE: June 15, 1950",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, San Francisco",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SUBJECT:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Yuba City, California",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "RESEARCH",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Rebulet 6-5-50.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Subject was located 6-13-50 residing at [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "San Jose, California. He was interviewed by SA [REDACTED] of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "this Office, who carefully explained the jurisdiction of the FBI to him",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "and questioned him relative to any information he might have which would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "be of interest to this Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] had nothing to add to his previous story as submitted",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "by letter to the Bureau on 4-9-50. He was advised that any information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "relative to \"flying saucers\" did not come within the jurisdiction of this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Bureau and that he could communicate such information to the Secretary of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "the Air Force, National Defense Building, The Pentagon, Washington 25,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "For the further information of the Bureau, Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "[REDACTED], was contacted in an effort to locate Mr. [REDACTED] Mr.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "[REDACTED] described [REDACTED] as being \"odd\" but would not elaborate on this",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "statement.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "It was also ascertained from [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "[REDACTED], San Jose, California, through whom [REDACTED] was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "located, that [REDACTED] was given to weird imaginings. Mr. [REDACTED] stated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "that he would not exactly describe [REDACTED] as being insane but stated that he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "was getting along in years and was prone to exaggerate on queer imaginings.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "It was the observation of the interviewing agent that Mr. [REDACTED] is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "abnormal mentally.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
